DDeessccrriippttiioonn
       text2  is run with to verify that the resolution and modes
       configured on vt01 (tty01) and vt02 (tty02)  display  cor-
       rectly.

   OOppttiioonnss
       The  following options are supported: display this message
       on stderr.  use smooth scrolling instead  of  window  jump
       scrolling.   display  only font number num.  start display
       from font number num.  ELI "-fs" use font server to  scale
       fonts  when  possible.   display  only  the font with this
       fontname.  do NOT free the font after printing.  Keep them
       all open.  exit after displaying all fonts.  Otherwise the
       window remains.  display ALL the glyphs of the font.  ver-
       bose  mode.   Printout  more  statistics  to stderr.  List
       names of fonts when displaying.  use  a  stipple  pattern.
       draw  stipple with Opaque Fill style.  use a tile pattern.
       If Opaque requested means FillSolid.  use named color  for
       foreground.   use  named  color for background.  use named
       color for tile foreground.  use named color for tile back-
       ground.  use this specified bitmap for stipple or tile.

   KKeeyyssttrrookkeess
       stop  drawing.   To  restart, cause an expose event.  exit
       stop drawing.  To restart, cause an expose event.

